The Telegraph - Calcutta : International

 UK veil ban

 London, Feb. 21 (PTI): A British schoolgirl today lost a legal challenge to her schools ban on a full-face veil. Justice Silber ruled that the ban was proportionate in the light of factors like the veil prevented teachers from seeing a pupils facial expression. 




